CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 16, 1961, pg. A3 reads: " 'New Era' Dawns at Herron Hill Junior High"
TitMainTitle: Three young women, including one wearing light colored hair barrettes, eyeglasses, and light colored blouse with poodle dog brooch on left collar, looking at open book on table, gathered in Herron Hill Junior High School classroom with chalkboard and world map
